00:15:53.920 --> 00:15:57.184
Imagine having a toothache that never goes away.

00:15:57.280 --> 00:16:03.040
Theo Jett's toothache turned into a tumour leading to 10 years of pain and isolation.

00:16:03.104 --> 00:16:09.664
When Mercy ships arrived in Madagascar, Theo Jett made a courageous three-day journey to the hospital ship.

00:16:09.472 --> 00:16:14.592
Volunteer surgeons removed her tumour, restored her health and renewed her hope.

00:16:14.304 --> 00:16:18.592
Your gift could bring life-changing surgery to people still waiting.

